Accept: application/json

###

POST {{CustomerOrderSystem_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Doe",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+15550001"
}

### Orders
GET {{CustomerOrderSystem_HostAddress}}/api/orders/customer/1
Accept: application/json

###

POST {{CustomerOrderSystem_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "status": "Pending"
}

### OrderItems
